To compile the binner application, run "make".

To install the binner into a directory of your choice, copy the files "mcmc.pl"
and "c/mcmc-core" into a directory contained in your PATH. Optionally, also copy
the accessory script test_binner.pl.


To test the binner application, run "make test". The tests require the presence of the "test-data" directory, whose contents can be downloaded at our website:

http://ecotheory.biology.gatech.edu/downloads/likelybin


This archive must be unpacked into this directory.
